      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a void. the quiet isn't peaceful, it's just empty. i keep thinking about how easy it would be to just... not be part of the system anymore. not even a break, but just a complete exit. like, if i'm already a ghost, would it even be a tragedy to finally stop haunting this place? would anything actually change?",
